Changes=This version includes the Java3D classes and native libraries (32 and 64 bit) for Windows, Linux and Mac OSX. No special installation is required as the Java3D system loads the correct native library automatically. Users of Oracle Java 1.7 under Mac OSX should read the "MessageToDisplayOnInstallation" entry. More information about the updated version of Java3D used in this package can be found at http://gouessej.wordpress.com/2012/08/01/java-3d-est-de-retour-java-3d-is-back and http://jogamp.org/wiki/index.php/Downloading_and_installing_JOGL.

